OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Malawi has asked boxing star Mike Tyson
OL,6, to become the official ambassador for  
OL,7, the country's cannabis crop.           
OL,9,FAgriculture Minister Lobin Low sent a  
OL,10,Fletter to Tyson inviting him to take up
OL,11,Fthe role, and said legalisation in     
OL,12,FMalawi had created new opportunities.  
OL,14,FTyson, a former world heavyweight      
OL,15,Fchampion, is an entrepreneur and has   
OL,16,Finvested in a cannabis farm in the US. 
OL,18,FBut the move has been criticised by    
OL,19,Fsome as the former boxer was imprisoned
OL,20,Ffor sex offences in the 1990s.         
